BonfyreIndex — artifact family index & search

Usage:
  bonfyre-index build <dir> [--db F]      Crawl & index artifact.json files
  bonfyre-index search <q> [--type T]      Search families
  bonfyre-index reuse [--db F]             Find shared atoms/operators
  bonfyre-index equivalence [--db F]       Show canonical-equivalent families
  bonfyre-index collapse-preview [--db F]  Preview safe equivalence collapse groups
  bonfyre-index confidence-preview [--db F] Preview exact/probable/related family groups
  bonfyre-index collapse-plan [--db F]     Choose deterministic keep/fold representatives
  bonfyre-index collapse-ledger <out> [--db F] Write non-destructive collapse action ledger
  bonfyre-index merge-manifest <out> [--db F] Write preview-only merge manifest artifact
  bonfyre-index bundle-layout <merge> <out> Build preview-only canonical bundle layout
  bonfyre-index validate-preview <path>    Validate preview-only merge/layout artifact
  bonfyre-index bundle-diff <layout> <out> Compare current disk state to projected bundle layout
  Add --json to the preview commands for machine-readable output
  bonfyre-index stats [--db F]             Summary statistics
